MOUTHWATERING Frites! ✨🍟👅

Frites cravings? Stop searching! Indulge at @superfrites for our irresistible triple-cooked Belgian-style frites, organic potatoes, crafted with 100% grass-fed beef tallow. Join us now!

✨ Toppings to choose from: 
 🔸 Pickled onions
 🔸 Smoked Pepper Mayo
 🔸 Cotija Cheese
 🔸 Cilantro

🙏🏻 Much love to @superfrites for treating me to their amazing frites! If you're craving bold flavors that will take your taste buds on an unforgettable journey, your search ends here!🔍💥

📍 777 S Alameda St, Los Angeles, CA
(Located in a stall inside Smorgasburg, 10am-4pm)
